title: BelowDeck: One Stew Over The Cuckoo’s Nest
description:
It's another night out with the cavemen on this week's "Below Deck," and this time around, Smashton is drunk, horny, AND violent. It's enough to make a head stew quit. Luckily, we'll always have Master Pierson.
